{"word":"Leprosy","slug":"leprosy","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Leprosy</b> Law concerning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=13'>Lev 13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=22&verse=4'>Lev 22:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=5&verse=3'>Num 5:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=12&verse=14'>Num 12:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=24&verse=8'>Deu 24:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=8&verse=4'>Mat 8:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=5&verse=14'>Luk 5:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=17&verse=14'>Luk 17:14</a><br/> Sent as a judgment:<br/> - On Miriam<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=12&verse=10'>Num 12:10</a> <br/> - On Gehazi<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=5&verse=27'>2Ki 5:27</a> <br/> - On Uzziah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=26&verse=21'>2Ch 26:21</a> <br/> Entailed<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=5&verse=27'>2Ki 5:27</a><br/> Isolation of lepers<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=13&verse=46'>Lev 13:46</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=5&verse=2'>Num 5:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=12&verse=14'>Num 12:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=15&verse=5'>2Ki 15:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=26&verse=21'>2Ch 26:21</a><br/> Separate burial of lepers<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=26&verse=23'>2Ch 26:23</a><br/> Instances of leprosy not mentioned above:<br/> - Four lepers outside Samaria<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=7&verse=3'>2Ki 7:3</a> <br/> - Azariah<br/> <a hre